# Face Verification API - Example Requests

## Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

## Face Verification with Valid Booking
POST http://localhost:3000/api/face-verify
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="face.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="eventId"

66148a2c1b2c3d4e5f6g7h8i
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

## Face Verification - Missing Image (Error Case)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/face-verify
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="eventId"

66148a2c1b2c3d4e5f6g7h8i
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

## Face Verification - Invalid EventId (Error Case)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/face-verify
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="face.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="eventId"

invalid-id
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

# Using cURL

## Health Check
# curl http://localhost:3000/health

## Face Verification
# curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/face-verify \
#   -F "image=@test-image.jpg" \
#   -F "eventId=66148a2c1b2c3d4e5f6g7h8i"

## Performance Test with Apache Bench
# ab -n 100 -c 10 -p data.json -T application/json http://localhost:3000/api/face-verify

## Performance Test with wrk
# wrk -t4 -c100 -d30s -s script.lua http://localhost:3000/api/face-verify
